item.title: CVE-2024-22137|2024-01-12T23:20:31.258Z -- MailMunch -- Constant Contact Forms by MailMunch
item.description: Improper Neutralization of Input During Web Page Generation ('Cross-site Scripting') vulnerability in MailMunch Constant Contact Forms by MailMunch allows Stored XSS.This issue affects Constant Contact Forms by MailMunch: from n/a through 2.0.11.
